<h4 class="title text-sm px-3 py-5 lg:px-8 font-normal tracking-widest uppercase">Most Read</h4>
<div class="flex flex-col px-2 lg:px-8 most-read">
<a class="p-2 py-3 border-b border-gray" href="https://sofrep.com/news/mighty-excalibur-game-changing-artillery-in-ukraine">
<span class="flex items-center">
<span class="text-4xl font-bold">1</span>
<p class="px-6 text-sm leading-tight flex-grow">Mighty Excalibur: Game Changing Artillery in Ukraine</p>
<img data-src="https://i0.wp.com/cms.sofrep.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/excaliburdarktech1.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1&resize=400,220" class="object-cover rounded w-16 h-16 lazy" alt="Mighty Excalibur: Game Changing Artillery in Ukraine">
</span>
</a>
<a class="p-2 py-3 border-b border-gray" href="https://sofrep.com/news/germany-prevents-spain-from-sending-tanks-to-ukraine">
<span class="flex items-center">
<span class="text-4xl font-bold">2</span>
<p class="px-6 text-sm leading-tight flex-grow">Germany Prevents Spain From Sending Tanks to Ukraine</p>
<img data-src="https://i0.wp.com/cms.sofrep.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/German-Leopard.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1&resize=400,220" class="object-cover rounded w-16 h-16 lazy" alt="Germany Prevents Spain From Sending Tanks to Ukraine">
